original_title: Tapak Dewata - Path of the Gods: Java and Bali
overview: A 1979 documentary on Java and Bali, written and directed by Phillip Noyce. The end credits say this film was produced for QANTAS Airways, which suggests it was used as some sort of promotional piece for travel to these particular locations.
title: Tapak Dewata - Path of the Gods: Java and Bali
